Known Bugs:
===========

Actually, there isen't any.  But:

* The program WordWorth4SE calls the CloseWorkbench() function twice...  So
  the request asking if you want to close the Workbench appears twice
  simultanousnly...
* A friend told me that Sim City could crash when CloseWbPatch is active.  He
  did me a demo.  But I really think that Sim City is very bad programmed.  It
  totally trashes the workbench display...  And don't forget: it's only a game.


